{"id": "app_dashboard_001", "category": "apps_tools", "sub_type": "dashboard", "difficulty": "easy", "language": "en", "prompt": "Create a sales dashboard in a single HTML file. Display 4 stat cards at the top: Total Revenue ($45,230), Orders (342), Customers (156), Conversion Rate (3.2%). Below, a simple bar chart using colored div bars showing monthly sales for Jan-Jun (values: 5200, 6800, 4900, 7200, 8100, 6500). Include a table below with top 5 products (name, units sold, revenue). Clean white design with blue accent.", "response": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <title>Sales Dashboard</title>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: sans-serif; background: #f7fafc; color: #172033; margin: 24px; }\n    .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(120px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; }\n    .card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #dbe3ef; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; }\n    svg { width: 100%; height: 260px; margin-top: 24px; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <main>\n    <h1>Sales Dashboard</h1>\n    <section class=\"cards\">\n      <article class=\"card\"><strong>Total Revenue</strong><p>$45,230</p></article>\n      <article class=\"card\"><strong>Orders</strong><p>342</p></article>\n      <article class=\"card\"><strong>Customers</strong><p>156</p></article>\n      <article class=\"card\"><strong>Conversion Rate</strong><p>3.2%</p></article>\n    </section>\n    <svg role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Monthly sales bar chart\" viewBox=\"0 0 700 260\">\n      <text x=\"20\" y=\"28\">Monthly Sales</text>\n      <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"640\" y2=\"220\" stroke=\"#91a4bd\"></line>\n      <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"220\" stroke=\"#91a4bd\"></line>\n      <rect x=\"90\" y=\"150\" width=\"48\" height=\"70\" fill=\"#1769aa\"></rect>\n      <rect x=\"180\" y=\"118\" width=\"48\" height=\"102\" fill=\"#1769aa\"></rect>\n      <rect x=\"270\" y=\"86\" width=\"48\" height=\"134\" fill=\"#1769aa\"></rect>\n      <rect x=\"360\" y=\"104\" width=\"48\" height=\"116\" fill=\"#1769aa\"></rect>\n      <rect x=\"450\" y=\"62\" width=\"48\" height=\"158\" fill=\"#1769aa\"></rect>\n      <rect x=\"540\" y=\"76\" width=\"48\" height=\"144\" fill=\"#1769aa\"></rect>\n      <text x=\"90\" y=\"242\">Jan</text><text x=\"180\" y=\"242\">Feb</text>\n      <text x=\"270\" y=\"242\">Mar</text><text x=\"360\" y=\"242\">Apr</text>\n      <text x=\"450\" y=\"242\">May</text><text x=\"540\" y=\"242\">Jun</text>\n    </svg>\n  </main>\n</body>\n</html>"}
